<verse eid="1CO 5:11"/><verse number="12" style="v" sid="1CO 5:12"/><char style="w" closed="true" strong="G1063">Porque</char> ¿<char style="w" closed="true" strong="G5101">qué</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G3427">me va á mí</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G2919">en juzgar</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G3588">á los</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G1854">que están fuera</char>? ¿<char style="w" closed="true" strong="G3780">No</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G2919">juzgáis</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G5210">vosotros</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G3588">á los</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G2080">que están dentro</char>? 
<verse eid="1CO 5:12"/><verse number="13" style="v" sid="1CO 5:13"/><char style="w" closed="true" strong="G1161">Porque</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G3588">á los</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G1854">que están fuera</char>, <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G2316">Dios</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G2919">juzgará</char>: <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G1808">quitad</char> <char style="add" closed="true">pues</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G3588">á ese</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G4190">malo</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G1537">de</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G5216">entre vosotros</char>.  
