<verse eid="1CO 12:28"/><verse number="29" style="v" sid="1CO 12:29"/>¿<char style="w" closed="true" strong="G3956">Son todos</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G0652">apóstoles</char>? ¿<char style="w" closed="true" strong="G3956">son todos</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G4396">profetas</char>? ¿<char style="w" closed="true" strong="G3956">todos</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G1320">doctores</char>? ¿<char style="w" closed="true" strong="G3956">todos</char> <char style="w" closed="true" strong="G1411">facultades</char>? 
